item.description: SoftLayer_Layout_Profile_Preference Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Layout_Profile_Preference contains definitions for layout preferences Local createDate Timestamp of when the preference was created Type: dateTime defaultValueFlag Indicates whether this is a default value or not Type: integer layoutContainerId The id of the related [[SoftLayer_Layout_Container]] Type: integer layoutItemId The id of the related [[SoftLayer_Layout_Item]] Type: integer layoutPreferenceId The internal identifier of the overridden [[SoftLayer_Layout_Preference]] Type: integer
